{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.1","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:1","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.017.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">\u00c9lie devant Achab. Les proph\u00e8tes de Baal<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-15: cf. (J\u00e9 38:7-13; 39:15-18.) Ps 112:1, 5-9.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Bien des jours s\u2019\u00e9coul\u00e8rent, et la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut ainsi adress\u00e9e \u00e0 \u00c9lie, dans la troisi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e: Va, pr\u00e9sente-toi devant Achab, et je ferai tomber de la pluie sur la face du sol.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.2","name":"1 Rois 18:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.17.24","name":"1 Rois 17:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.17.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.2","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:2","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Et \u00c9lie alla, pour se pr\u00e9senter devant Achab. La famine \u00e9tait grande \u00e0 Samarie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.3","name":"1 Rois 18:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.1","name":"1 Rois 18:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.3","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:3","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Et Achab fit appeler Abdias, chef de sa maison. Or Abdias craignait beaucoup l\u2019\u00c9ternel;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.4","name":"1 Rois 18:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.2","name":"1 Rois 18:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.4","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:4","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>et lorsque J\u00e9zabel extermina les proph\u00e8tes de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, Abdias prit cent proph\u00e8tes qu\u2019il cacha cinquante par cinquante dans une caverne, et il les avait nourris de pain et d\u2019eau.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.5","name":"1 Rois 18:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.3","name":"1 Rois 18:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.5","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:5","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Achab dit \u00e0 Abdias: Va par le pays vers toutes les sources d\u2019eau et vers tous les torrents; peut-\u00eatre se trouvera-t-il de l\u2019herbe, et nous conserverons la vie aux chevaux et aux mulets, et nous n\u2019aurons pas besoin d\u2019abattre du b\u00e9tail.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.6","name":"1 Rois 18:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.4","name":"1 Rois 18:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.6","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:6","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Ils se partag\u00e8rent le pays pour le parcourir; Achab alla seul par un chemin, et Abdias alla seul par un autre chemin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.7","name":"1 Rois 18:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.5","name":"1 Rois 18:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.7","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:7","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Comme Abdias \u00e9tait en route, voici, \u00c9lie le rencontra. Abdias, l\u2019ayant reconnu, tomba sur son visage, et dit: Est-ce toi, mon seigneur \u00c9lie?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.8","name":"1 Rois 18:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.6","name":"1 Rois 18:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.8","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:8","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Il lui r\u00e9pondit: C\u2019est moi; va, dis \u00e0 ton ma\u00eetre: Voici \u00c9lie!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.9","name":"1 Rois 18:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.7","name":"1 Rois 18:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.9","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:9","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Et Abdias dit: Quel p\u00e9ch\u00e9 ai-je commis, pour que tu livres ton serviteur entre les mains d\u2019Achab, qui me fera mourir?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.10","name":"1 Rois 18:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.8","name":"1 Rois 18:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.10","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:10","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel est vivant! Il n\u2019est ni nation ni royaume o\u00f9 mon ma\u00eetre n\u2019ait envoy\u00e9 pour te chercher; et quand on disait que tu n\u2019y \u00e9tais pas, il faisait jurer le royaume et la nation que l\u2019on ne t\u2019avait pas trouv\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.11","name":"1 Rois 18:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.9","name":"1 Rois 18:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.11","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:11","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Et maintenant tu dis: Va, dis \u00e0 ton ma\u00eetre: Voici \u00c9lie!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.12","name":"1 Rois 18:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.10","name":"1 Rois 18:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.12","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:12","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Puis, lorsque je t\u2019aurai quitt\u00e9 l\u2019esprit de l\u2019\u00c9ternel te transportera je ne sais o\u00f9; et j\u2019irai informer Achab, qui ne te trouvera pas, et qui me tuera. Cependant ton serviteur craint l\u2019\u00c9ternel d\u00e8s sa jeunesse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.13","name":"1 Rois 18:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.11","name":"1 Rois 18:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.13","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:13","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>N\u2019a-t-on pas dit \u00e0 mon seigneur ce que j\u2019ai fait quand J\u00e9zabel tua les proph\u00e8tes de l\u2019\u00c9ternel? J\u2019ai cach\u00e9 cent proph\u00e8tes de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, cinquante par cinquante dans une caverne, et je les ai nourris de pain et d\u2019eau.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.14","name":"1 Rois 18:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.12","name":"1 Rois 18:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.14","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:14","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Et maintenant tu dis: Va, dis \u00e0 ton ma\u00eetre: Voici \u00c9lie! Il me tuera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.15","name":"1 Rois 18:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.13","name":"1 Rois 18:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.15","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:15","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Mais \u00c9lie dit: L\u2019\u00c9ternel des arm\u00e9es, dont je suis le serviteur, est vivant! Aujourd\u2019hui je me pr\u00e9senterai devant Achab.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.16","name":"1 Rois 18:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.14","name":"1 Rois 18:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.16","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:16","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.017,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 16-40: cf. 2 Ch 28:19. (Mt 6:24. Jos 24:15. J\u00e9 10:1-16. 2 Ch 7:1-3.) Ps 97:7. De 13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Abdias, \u00e9tant all\u00e9 \u00e0 la rencontre d\u2019Achab, l\u2019informa de la chose. Et Achab se rendit au-devant d\u2019\u00c9lie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.17","name":"1 Rois 18:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.15","name":"1 Rois 18:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.17","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:17","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>A peine Achab aper\u00e7ut-il \u00c9lie qu\u2019il lui dit: Est-ce toi, qui jettes le trouble en Isra\u00ebl?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.18","name":"1 Rois 18:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.16","name":"1 Rois 18:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.18","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:18","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>\u00c9lie r\u00e9pondit: Je ne trouble point Isra\u00ebl; c\u2019est toi, au contraire, et la maison de ton p\u00e8re, puisque vous avez abandonn\u00e9 les commandements de l\u2019\u00c9ternel et que tu es all\u00e9 apr\u00e8s les Baals.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.19","name":"1 Rois 18:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.17","name":"1 Rois 18:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.19","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:19","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Fais maintenant rassembler tout Isra\u00ebl aupr\u00e8s de moi, \u00e0 la montagne du Carmel, et aussi les quatre cent cinquante proph\u00e8tes de Baal et les quatre cents proph\u00e8tes d\u2019Astart\u00e9 qui mangent \u00e0 la table de J\u00e9zabel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.20","name":"1 Rois 18:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.18","name":"1 Rois 18:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.20","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:20","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Achab envoya des messagers vers tous les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et il rassembla les proph\u00e8tes \u00e0 la montagne du Carmel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.21","name":"1 Rois 18:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.19","name":"1 Rois 18:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.21","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:21","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Alors \u00c9lie s\u2019approcha de tout le peuple, et dit: Jusqu\u2019\u00e0 quand clocherez-vous des deux c\u00f4t\u00e9s? Si l\u2019\u00c9ternel est Dieu, allez apr\u00e8s lui; si c\u2019est Baal, allez apr\u00e8s lui! Le peuple ne lui r\u00e9pondit rien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.22","name":"1 Rois 18:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.20","name":"1 Rois 18:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.22","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:22","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Et \u00c9lie dit au peuple: Je suis rest\u00e9 seul des proph\u00e8tes de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et il y a quatre cent cinquante proph\u00e8tes de Baal.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.23","name":"1 Rois 18:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.21","name":"1 Rois 18:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.23","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:23","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Que l\u2019on nous donne deux taureaux; qu\u2019ils choisissent pour eux l\u2019un des taureaux, qu\u2019ils le coupent par morceaux, et qu\u2019ils le placent sur le bois, sans y mettre le feu; et moi, je pr\u00e9parerai l\u2019autre taureau, et je le placerai sur le bois, sans y mettre le feu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.24","name":"1 Rois 18:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.22","name":"1 Rois 18:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.24","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:24","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Puis invoquez le nom de votre dieu; et moi, j\u2019invoquerai le nom de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Le dieu qui r\u00e9pondra par le feu, c\u2019est celui-l\u00e0 qui sera Dieu. Et tout le peuple r\u00e9pondit, en disant: C\u2019est bien!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.25","name":"1 Rois 18:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.23","name":"1 Rois 18:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.25","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:25","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>\u00c9lie dit aux proph\u00e8tes de Baal: Choisissez pour vous l\u2019un des taureaux, pr\u00e9parez-le les premiers, car vous \u00eates les plus nombreux, et invoquez le nom de votre dieu; mais ne mettez pas le feu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.26","name":"1 Rois 18:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.24","name":"1 Rois 18:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.26","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:26","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Ils prirent le taureau qu\u2019on leur donna, et le pr\u00e9par\u00e8rent; et ils invoqu\u00e8rent le nom de Baal, depuis le matin jusqu\u2019\u00e0 midi, en disant: Baal r\u00e9ponds nous! Mais il n\u2019y eut ni voix ni r\u00e9ponse. Et ils sautaient devant l\u2019autel qu\u2019ils avaient fait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.27","name":"1 Rois 18:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.25","name":"1 Rois 18:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.27","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:27","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>A midi, \u00c9lie se moqua d\u2019eux, et dit: Criez \u00e0 haute voix, puisqu\u2019il est dieu; il pense \u00e0 quelque chose, ou il est occup\u00e9, ou il est en voyage; peut-\u00eatre qu\u2019il dort, et il se r\u00e9veillera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.28","name":"1 Rois 18:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.26","name":"1 Rois 18:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.28","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:28","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Et ils cri\u00e8rent \u00e0 haute voix, et ils se firent, selon leur coutume, des incisions avec des \u00e9p\u00e9es et avec des lances, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que le sang coul\u00e2t sur eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.29","name":"1 Rois 18:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.27","name":"1 Rois 18:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.29","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:29","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Lorsque midi fut pass\u00e9, ils proph\u00e9tis\u00e8rent jusqu\u2019au moment de la pr\u00e9sentation de l\u2019offrande. Mais il n\u2019y eut ni voix, ni r\u00e9ponse, ni signe d\u2019attention.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.30","name":"1 Rois 18:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.28","name":"1 Rois 18:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.30","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:30","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>\u00c9lie dit alors \u00e0 tout le peuple: Approchez-vous de moi! Tout le peuple s\u2019approcha de lui. Et \u00c9lie r\u00e9tablit l\u2019autel de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, qui avait \u00e9t\u00e9 renvers\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.31","name":"1 Rois 18:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.29","name":"1 Rois 18:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.31","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:31","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Il prit douze pierres d\u2019apr\u00e8s le nombre des tribus des fils de Jacob, auquel l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait dit: Isra\u00ebl sera ton nom;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.32","name":"1 Rois 18:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.30","name":"1 Rois 18:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.32","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:32","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>et il b\u00e2tit avec ces pierres un autel au nom de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Il fit autour de l\u2019autel un foss\u00e9 de la capacit\u00e9 de deux mesures de semence.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.33","name":"1 Rois 18:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.31","name":"1 Rois 18:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.33","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:33","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Il arrangea le bois, coupa le taureau par morceaux, et le pla\u00e7a sur le bois.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.34","name":"1 Rois 18:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.32","name":"1 Rois 18:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.34","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:34","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Puis il dit: Remplissez d\u2019eau quatre cruches, et versez-les sur l\u2019holocauste et sur le bois. Il dit: Faites-le une seconde fois. Et ils le firent une seconde fois. Il dit: Faites-le une troisi\u00e8me fois. Et ils le firent une troisi\u00e8me fois.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.35","name":"1 Rois 18:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.33","name":"1 Rois 18:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.35","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:35","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>L\u2019eau coula autour de l\u2019autel, et l\u2019on remplit aussi d\u2019eau le foss\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.36","name":"1 Rois 18:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.34","name":"1 Rois 18:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.36","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:36","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Au moment de la pr\u00e9sentation de l\u2019offrande, \u00c9lie, le proph\u00e8te, s\u2019avan\u00e7a et dit: \u00c9ternel, Dieu d\u2019Abraham, d\u2019Isaac et d\u2019Isra\u00ebl! Que l\u2019on sache aujourd\u2019hui que tu es Dieu en Isra\u00ebl, que je suis ton serviteur, et que j\u2019ai fait toutes ces choses par ta parole!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.37","name":"1 Rois 18:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.35","name":"1 Rois 18:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.37","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:37","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>R\u00e9ponds-moi, \u00c9ternel, r\u00e9ponds-moi, afin que ce peuple reconnaisse que c\u2019est toi, \u00c9ternel, qui es Dieu, et que c\u2019est toi qui ram\u00e8nes leur c\u0153ur!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.38","name":"1 Rois 18:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.36","name":"1 Rois 18:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.38","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:38","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Et le feu de l\u2019\u00c9ternel tomba, et il consuma l\u2019holocauste, le bois, les pierres et la terre, et il absorba l\u2019eau qui \u00e9tait dans le foss\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.39","name":"1 Rois 18:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.37","name":"1 Rois 18:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.39","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:39","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Quand tout le peuple vit cela, ils tomb\u00e8rent sur leur visage et dirent: C\u2019est l\u2019\u00c9ternel qui est Dieu! C\u2019est l\u2019\u00c9ternel qui est Dieu!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.40","name":"1 Rois 18:40","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.38","name":"1 Rois 18:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.40","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:40","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>Saisissez les proph\u00e8tes de Baal, leur dit \u00c9lie; qu\u2019aucun d\u2019eux n\u2019\u00e9chappe! Et ils les saisirent. \u00c9lie les fit descendre au torrent de Kison, o\u00f9 il les \u00e9gorgea.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.41","name":"1 Rois 18:41","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.39","name":"1 Rois 18:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.41","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:41","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.042,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La pluie<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 41-46: cf. Ja 5:16-18.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup>Et \u00c9lie dit \u00e0 Achab: Monte, mange et bois; car il se fait un bruit qui annonce la pluie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.42","name":"1 Rois 18:42","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.40","name":"1 Rois 18:40","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.42","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:42","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.043,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup>Achab monta pour manger et pour boire. Mais \u00c9lie monta au sommet du Carmel; et, se penchant contre terre, il mit son visage entre ses genoux,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.43","name":"1 Rois 18:43","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.43"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.41","name":"1 Rois 18:41","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"43","lastverse":"43","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.43","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.43","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:43","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.044,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.43\" class=\"v\">43<\/sup>et dit \u00e0 son serviteur: Monte, regarde du c\u00f4t\u00e9 de la mer. Le serviteur monta, il regarda, et dit: Il n\u2019y a rien. \u00c9lie dit sept fois: Retourne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.44","name":"1 Rois 18:44","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.44"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.42","name":"1 Rois 18:42","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"44","lastverse":"44","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.44","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.44","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:44","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.045,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.44\" class=\"v\">44<\/sup>A la septi\u00e8me fois, il dit: Voici un petit nuage qui s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve de la mer, et qui est comme la paume de la main d\u2019un homme. \u00c9lie dit: Monte, et dis \u00e0 Achab: Attelle et descends, afin que la pluie ne t\u2019arr\u00eate pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.45","name":"1 Rois 18:45","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.45"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.43","name":"1 Rois 18:43","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"45","lastverse":"45","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.45","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.45","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:45","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.044,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.046,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.45\" class=\"v\">45<\/sup>En peu d\u2019instants, le ciel s\u2019obscurcit par les nuages, le vent s\u2019\u00e9tablit, et il y eut une forte pluie. Achab monta sur son char, et partit pour Jizreel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.46","name":"1 Rois 18:46","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.46"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.44","name":"1 Rois 18:44","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.44"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"46","lastverse":"46","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.46","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.46","label":"","reference":"1 Rois 18:46","prev_osis_id":"1Kgs.018.045,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.019.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Kgs.18.46\" class=\"v\">46<\/sup>Et la main de l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut sur \u00c9lie, qui se ceignit les reins et courut devant Achab jusqu\u2019\u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e de Jizreel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18","name":"1 Rois 18","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.19.1","name":"1 Rois 19:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.19.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.45","name":"1 Rois 18:45","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.18.45"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||